### Create Service
POST http://localhost:8080/api/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mens Haircut",
  "description": "Standard mens haircut with wash",
  "durationMinutes": 30,
  "price": 25.00,
  "active": true
}

### Get All Services
GET http://localhost:8080/api/services

### Get Active Services
GET http://localhost:8080/api/services/active

### Get Service by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/services/1

### Update Service
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/services/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Premium Mens Haircut",
  "description": "Premium haircut with hot towel treatment",
  "durationMinutes": 45,
  "price": 35.00,
  "active": true
}

### Deactivate Service
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/services/1/deactivate

### Delete Service
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/services/1